# UICloseSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
Dismisses a UI element on demand. Returns early until SandboxConfigSingletonComponent is present.
When the close button is released (a UIOnReleaseOneFrameComponent whose element id matches the close
button), it finds the close-target element by UUID and emits a UIDestroyOneFrameComponent, which
UIControlSystem turns into a deferred destroy of that element and its children.

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SandboxConfigSingletonComponent | read | Close button and close-target ids; guard |
| UIOnReleaseOneFrameComponent | read | Release on the close button triggers the dismiss |
| BaseComponent | read | Locates the close-target element by UUID |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| UIDestroyOneFrameComponent | add (oneframe) | Emitted on the close-target element to destroy it |
